author: Second Wind
description:
This video is brought to you by Guards II: Chaos in Hell, the upcoming turn-based tactics game with extremely simple rules, but even more extremely deep mechanics. Check out the demo on Steam today – https://store.steampowered.com/app/2958570/Guards_II_Chaos_in_Hell/

Jack and Nick fight demons one turn at a time in Guards II: Chaos in Hell.

title: Surviving the Depths of Guards II: Chaos in Hell w/ Jack and Nick

author: Second Wind
description:
This video is brought to you by GameMaker, the free, fast, and easy-to-use 2D game engine that’s helped power modern classics like UFO 50, Antonblast, and Yahtzee’s Starstruck Vagabond – https://opr.as/SecondWind-3

On this week’s episode of Windbreaker, Yahtzee, JM8, and Marty celebrate the start of "E3" season by chatting about the advertising -- trailers, print ads, features, interviews, demos, and more -- that actually worked on them in the past.
